{"tid":846152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民叫人去大灣區啊 罪大惡極","createTime":"2018-10-03T07:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T09:43:24.000Z","uid":38523,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef5dc0d491a85be3447f8d982ed1bfcf854865b1","tid":846152,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"保皇狗呢睇唔到<br />\n咁身體力行去大陸搵錢呢？<br />\n哎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 駁唔到<br />\n你話你去大陸做教師姐<br />\n點知係咪特攻訓練？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/190048_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F190048_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=34776b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/190050_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F190050_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b83673cb&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關愛座hunter: 夠膽你出來比我點你相<br />\n等我send比大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d945f0a48f643129f91c48ec56eea647c34b79e","tid":846152,"uid":38523,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:04:07.000Z","msg":"關狗可以回應下未<br />\n先唔講保皇狗一樣叫人去大灣區<br />\n泛民&ldquo;叫&rdquo;人去大灣區 保皇狗又叫<br />\n仲要泛民支持特權調查沙中線<br />\n保皇狗反對<br />\n但你地一樣一直放生保皇狗<br />\n不過最重要既係你屌佢地&ldquo;叫&rdquo;人去大灣區<br />\n你自己就去身體最誠實去大陸搵埋錢<br />\n你都可以大大聲屌其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有冇咁無恥啊？<br />\n得出<br />\n要我出來比你點相啊嘛<br />\n你都傻<br />\n點知你係大陸個幾年係咪上特攻課程<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ef0ae650fb0f87d3891b32e2010e50557c4a7f","tid":846152,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kk39dBGPAt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fkk39dBGPAt4&d=y20W634u0Ambr8VjUlsI4TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a22462f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kk39dBGPAt4</a>"},{"pid":"2dc36a1ce07f88a72c295605981eec90e1a0d7e1","tid":846152,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77ef0ae650fb0f87d3891b32e2010e50557c4a7f","tid":846152,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kk39dBGPAt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fkk39dBGPAt4&d=y20W634u0Ambr8VjUlsI4TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a22462f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kk39dBGPAt4</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"冇人支持泛民<br />\n但起碼<br />\n沙中線調查<br />\n佢地支持<br />\n保皇狗反對<br />\n最可笑係呢班人仲當保皇狗隱形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口口聲聲話屌賣港<br />\n但最賣個班當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b2ad96deb967dc930fe489f5b8b379a5fbaa35","tid":846152,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"所以<br />\n我睇穿左呢班人<br />\n不論泛民做一次<br />\n兩次<br />\n次次都做出正確選擇<br />\n呢班人一樣會追屌而放生保皇狗<br />\n目的好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a30ac743cf6b55f8188831a3fff58ded4f7b68","tid":846152,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:18:50.000Z","msg":"負評班人咪又係關狗分身／打手<br />\n除左負評仲識乜<br />\n有邊個可以幫佢解釋到？"},{"pid":"fa9cfbd7f4ba6bb5693a9f5f3846abb061fdfbee","tid":846152,"uid":52651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:21:36.000Z","msg":"民主黨蔡耀昌最鐘意幫咩人呀？"},{"pid":"acdbe870b33ed2d8ca859409140ca7bdc5d9c0f7","tid":846152,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa9cfbd7f4ba6bb5693a9f5f3846abb061fdfbee","tid":846152,"uid":52651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:21:36.000Z","msg":"民主黨蔡耀昌最鐘意幫咩人呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"一件<br />\n之後呢？<br />\n講下你地保皇狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/182347_aad48f01731e016984a888c7e998dc38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F182347_aad48f01731e016984a888c7e998dc38.jpg&h=0e93b055&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba7d77907c0429a94e42f579d04ab0dcf5bd4837","tid":846152,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以關狗為首既保皇狗打手呢"},{"pid":"2baf91e6d9aa32614162206026d990a2f063d700","tid":846152,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T22:40:13.000Z","msg":"關狗<br />\n當睇唔到啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ac54c5213b2d6858d2267a4d2db03d345b8b66","tid":846152,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T22:48:48.000Z","msg":"關狗除左搵佢班五毛支持者負評外<br />\n仲識乜？<br />\n入來駁都唔敢？<br />\n咁又係<br />\n點駁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762bd4b9838aa652b94f83332671d591b62f489a","tid":846152,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}